(8, 'Maruti Suzuki Baleno Car 2024: A Premium Hatchback for Indian Roads', 'maruti-suzuki-baleno-car-2024-a-premium-hatchback-for-indian-roads', 'Automobile', 'upload/post/1735621584_post_thumbnail_1733208839_newsbaleno 2024 1.webp', 'Discover the Maruti Suzuki Baleno 2024, a premium hatchback offering style, performance, and efficiency. Explore its specs, advanced features like HUD and Suzuk', 'Maruti Suzuki Baleno 2024, Baleno Car Price India, Premium Hatchback, Baleno Mileage, Maruti Baleno Specs, Best Hatchback in India, Maruti Suzuki Features, New Baleno Price 2024', '<p>The Maruti Suzuki Baleno 2024 is a blend of style, performance, and efficiency, making it a strong contender in the premium hatchback segment in India. With advanced features, competitive pricing, and excellent mileage, it appeals to a wide range of car buyers.</p><h2>Engine and Performance</h2><ul><li><strong>Engine Options</strong>: 1.2L K-Series petrol (also available in CNG).</li><li><strong>Power Output</strong>: 88.5 BHP (petrol), 76.4 BHP (CNG).</li><li><strong>Torque</strong>: 113 Nm (petrol), 98.5 Nm (CNG).</li><li><strong>Transmission</strong>: 5-speed manual and AMT.</li><li><strong>Fuel Efficiency</strong>: 22.35 km/l (petrol), 30.61 km/kg (CNG).</li></ul><h2>Dimensions</h2><ul><li><strong>Length x Width x Height</strong>: 3,990 mm x 1,745 mm x 1,500 mm.</li><li><strong>Wheelbase</strong>: 2,520 mm.</li><li><strong>Boot Space</strong>: 318 liters.</li></ul><h2>Interior and Comfort</h2><ul><li><strong>Seating Capacity</strong>: 5 seats.</li><li><strong>Infotainment</strong>: 9-inch SmartPlay Pro+ touchscreen with wireless Android Auto and Apple CarPlay.</li><li><strong>Additional Features</strong>:<ul><li>Heads-up Display (HUD).</li><li>360-degree camera.</li><li>Rear AC vents.</li><li>Automatic climate control.</li><li>Suzuki Connect for connected car features.</li></ul></li></ul><h2>Safety</h2><ul><li><strong>Airbags</strong>: 6 (driver, passenger, side, curtain).</li><li><strong>Brakes</strong>: ABS with EBD and brake assist.</li><li><strong>Additional Safety Features</strong>:<ul><li>Hill hold assist.</li><li>ISOFIX child seat mounts.</li><li>ESP (Electronic Stability Program).</li></ul></li></ul><h2><img src=\"data:image/webp;base64,\" data-filename=\"download.webp\" style=\"width: 370px;\"><br>Exterior Design</h2><ul><li><strong>Lighting</strong>: LED projector headlamps with DRLs.</li><li><strong>Alloy Wheels</strong>: Precision-cut alloy wheels.</li><li><strong>Additional Features</strong>: UV cut glasses, body-colored ORVMs, rear spoiler.</li></ul><h2>Price Range</h2><p>Maruti Suzuki Baleno 2024 Price in India: ₹6.66 lakh to ₹9.83 lakh (ex-showroom).</p><h2>Why Choose the Baleno 2024?</h2><ul><li>Advanced tech features like HUD and Suzuki Connect.</li><li>Superior mileage for both petrol and CNG versions.</li><li>Spacious cabin with premium interiors.</li><li>Reliable safety features and excellent build quality.</li></ul>', 1, '2024-12-30 23:36:24', '2024-12-30 23:36:24');
