(22, 'Salman Khan Net Worth and Upcoming Movies', 'salman-khan-net-worth-and-upcoming-movies', 'Entertainment', 'upload/post/1735631407_post_thumbnail_Salman-Khan.webp', 'Discover Salman Khan\'s net worth of ₹2,900 crore and his exciting lineup of upcoming movies, including Singham Again, Kick 2, and Tiger vs Pathaan. Explore his', 'Salman Khan net worth, Salman Khan movies 2024, Baby John movie, Singham Again release date, Sikandar movie, Kick 2 updates, Tiger vs Pathaan release date, Bollywood actor Salman Khan', '<h5><b>Upcoming Movies of Salman Khan</b></h5><p>Salman Khan continues to captivate audiences with a lineup of highly anticipated projects. Here\'s a look at his upcoming films:</p><h4>1. Baby John</h4><ul><li><strong>Release Date:</strong> December 25, 2024<br>Salman Khan will make a special cameo in this film starring Varun Dhawan. The film is expected to be a festive blockbuster.<br><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"th.jpg\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><br></li></ul><h4>2. Singham Again</h4><ul><li><strong>Release Date:</strong> November 1, 2024<br>Directed by Rohit Shetty, this action-packed film sees Salman Khan in a pivotal role alongside Ajay Devgn in the celebrated <em>Singham</em> franchise.<br><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"th (1).jpg\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><br></li></ul><h4>3. Sikandar</h4><ul><li><strong>Release Date:</strong> 2025<br>Helmed by A.R. Murugadoss, this action thriller will feature Salman Khan in the lead role. The film promises to be a gripping tale of bravery and resilience.<br><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"th (2).jpg\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><br></li></ul><h4>4. Kick 2</h4><ul><li><strong>Release Date:</strong> 2025<br>A sequel to the 2014 blockbuster <em>Kick</em>, this film is currently in production and is expected to deliver the same thrill and excitement as its predecessor.<br><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"th (3).jpg\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><br></li></ul><h4>5. Tiger vs Pathaan</h4><ul><li><strong>Release Date:</strong> 2027<br>Arguably one of the most awaited films, this epic showdown will bring together Salman Khan as Tiger and Shah Rukh Khan as Pathaan. Fans are eagerly awaiting this cinematic extravaganza.<br><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"th (4).jpg\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><br></li></ul>', 1, '2024-12-31 02:20:07', '2025-01-01 03:57:27');
